---
---
<div class="panel ai-panel area-ai">
  <h2>✨ AI 引擎配置</h2>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;width:100%;margin-bottom:8px;">
    <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <label>API 接口地址</label>
      <input type="text" id="apiUrl" value="https://api.openai.com/v1" placeholder="https://..." style="width:100%;" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <label>API 密钥</label>
      <input type="password" id="apiKey" placeholder="sk-..." style="width:100%;" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="apiUrlHint" style="display:none;margin-bottom:8px;"></div>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;width:100%;margin-bottom:16px;">
    <button id="btnFetchModels" class="btn btn-fetch" style="margin:0;">🔄 拉取模型</button>
    <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <select id="modelSelect" style="width:100%;">
        <option value="">请先获取模型...</option>
      </select>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <div id="searchConfigBlock" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
    <div class="search-config-head">
      <label class="search-toggle-card" for="searchEnable">
        <input type="checkbox" id="searchEnable" />
        <span class="search-toggle-track" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="search-toggle-thumb"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="search-toggle-copy">
          <span class="search-toggle-title">🌐 联网搜索增强</span>
          <span class="search-toggle-subtitle">在生成前补充外部资料，提高设定参考质量</span>
        </span>
      </label>
      <span id="searchModeBadge" class="search-mode-badge" style="display: none;"></span>
    </div>

    <div id="searchConfigDetail" style="display: none;">
      <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 12px 0; line-height: 1.5;">
        开启后，AI 生成角色/世界书前会先搜索相关资料作为参考。<br/>
        <span style="color: var(--text-faint);">• 不填搜索 Key → 依赖 AI 模型自带联网能力（Gemini/Perplexity 等）</span><br/>
        <span style="color: var(--text-faint);">• 填写搜索 Key → 独立搜索引擎，结果更可靠</span>
      </p>

      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <label>搜索引擎</label>
        <select id="searchEngine">
          <option value="none" selected>不使用独立搜索（靠 AI 自身联网）</option>
          <option value="serper">Serper.dev（Google 结果 · 免费 2500次/月）</option>
          <option value="tavily">Tavily（AI 专用 · 免费 1000次/月）</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div id="searchKeyGroup" style="display: none;">
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
          <label id="searchKeyLabel">搜索 API Key</label>
          <input type="password" id="searchApiKey" placeholder="填入搜索引擎的 API Key..." />
        </div>
        <div id="searchRegisterHint" style="font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5;"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <label>搜索结果数量</label>
          <select id="searchResultCount">
            <option value="3">3 条</option>
            <option value="5" selected>5 条</option>
            <option value="8">8 条</option>
            <option value="12">12 条</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <label>搜索语言</label>
          <select id="searchLang">
            <option value="zh-CN" selected>中文</option>
            <option value="en">English</option>
            <option value="ja">日本語</option>
            <option value="auto">自动检测</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <label>自定义搜索词 <span style="font-weight: normal; color: var(--text-faint);">（留空则自动从提示词提取）</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="searchCustomQuery" placeholder="例如：赛博朋克 世界观 设定集..." />
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center;">
        <button id="btnTestSearch" class="btn btn-fetch" style="width: auto; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 0.78rem; margin: 0;">🔍 测试搜索</button>
        <span id="searchTestStatus" style="font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-muted);"></span>
      </div>

      <div id="searchPreview" style="display: none; margin-top: 10px; max-height: 200px; overflow-y: auto; background: var(--surface-overlay); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; font-size: 0.72rem;"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <div class="preset-upload">
    <label style="color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-2) 62%, var(--text-main)); margin-bottom: 8px; display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">📂 导入酒馆原生预设 (.json)</label>
    <input type="file" id="presetInput" accept=".json" />
    <div id="presetListContainer" style="display: none; max-height: 180px; overflow-y: auto; margin-top: 10px; background: var(--surface-overlay); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px;"></div>
    <div id="presetStatus" style="font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-muted);">
      导入预设后，可勾选要注入的文风和规则
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #apiUrlHint {
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }
  #apiUrlHint .hint-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: default;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  #apiUrlHint .hint-detail {
    display: none;
    padding: 6px 10px 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px;
    margin-top: -2px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  #apiUrlHint:hover .hint-detail {
    display: block;
  }

  #searchConfigBlock {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-cyan) 6%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  #searchConfigBlock.active {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-cyan) 10%, transparent);
  }

  .search-config-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .search-toggle-card {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    min-width: 0;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: var(--surface-elevated);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  .search-toggle-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.28);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.16);
  }

  .search-toggle-card.is-active {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.36);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12), transparent 42%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.5), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.86));
    box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.12);
  }

  .search-toggle-card input {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .search-toggle-track {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 28px;
    padding: 3px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--chip-border);
    background: var(--surface-overlay-strong);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    transition: border-color 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
  }

  .search-toggle-thumb {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-muted) 64%, white), color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-soft) 82%, transparent));
    box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.28);
    transform: translateX(0);
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
  }

  .search-toggle-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-width: 0;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .search-toggle-title {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .search-toggle-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .search-toggle-card.is-active .search-toggle-track {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.94), rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.88));
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .search-toggle-card.is-active .search-toggle-thumb {
    transform: translateX(20px);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a5f3fc, #38bdf8);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.32);
  }

  .search-mode-badge {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .search-config-head {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .search-mode-badge {
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .search-scan-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: inherit;
  }
  .search-scan-glass {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(56,189,248,0.7));
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .search-scan-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56,189,248,0.6), rgba(56,189,248,0.9), rgba(56,189,248,0.6), transparent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(56,189,248,0.5);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .search-scan-doc {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    opacity: 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(56,189,248,0.5));
  }

  .search-result-item {
    padding: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }
  .search-result-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .search-result-item:hover { background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.06); }
  .search-result-title {
    color: #38bdf8;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .search-result-snippet {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .search-result-url {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    margin-top: 2px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
</style>
